sentences.sentence: This is where you enter UNIX commands.
sentences.translation: 这正是您输入UNIX命令的地方。

sentences.sentence: All UNIX systems usually have one allocation of primary swap space.
sentences.translation: 所有unix系统通常都有一个主交换空间分配。

sentences.sentence: These applications will not run on UNIX.
sentences.translation: 这些应用程序不在UNIX上运行。
